{"type":"message","id":"bc04e5a0","parentId":"027018ed","timestamp":"2026-03-10T09:34:46.405Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:579e37a9-2778-4eac-9c91-54695d2cd1f1 task:579e37a9-2778-4eac-9c91-54695d2cd1f1] 诊断深渊代行者批注 API 的 502 错误。\n\n**问题现象**：\n- API 端点 `https://kuroneko.chat/api/annotations` 返回 502 Bad Gateway\n- 前端收到 HTML 错误页面而非 JSON（\"<!doctype\" 开头）\n\n**服务信息**（来自 HEARTBEAT.md）：\n- 服务名称: `abyss-annotation-api`\n- 端口: 3002\n- 管理: PM2\n- 代码位置: `/var/www/novel/abyss/api/server.js`\n- 数据位置: `/var/www/novel/abyss/api/data/annotations.json`\n\n**诊断步骤**：\n1. 检查 PM2 服务状态：`pm2 list` 和 `pm2 show abyss-annotation-api`\n2. 检查端口 3002 是否在监听：`netstat -tlnp | grep 3002` 或 `ss -tlnp | grep 3002`\n3. 检查 Nginx 配置：`cat /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/kuroneko.chat` 或类似配置文件，确认 /api/annotations 代理设置\n4. 如果服务挂了，尝试重启：`pm2 restart abyss-annotation-api`\n5. 查看服务日志：`pm2 logs abyss-annotation-api --lines 50`\n\n**期望输出**：\n1. 服务当前状态（运行中/停止/错误）\n2. 错误原因（如果找到）\n3. 修复操作（如果执行了）\n4. 修复后验证 API 是否正常响应\n\n**注意**：如果 PM2 中没有该服务，需要用 `pm2 start /var/www/novel/abyss/api/server.js --name abyss-annotation-api` 启动。\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 10th, 2026 — 5:34 PM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1773135286402}}
{"type":"message","id":"7b212491","parentId":"bc04e5a0","timestamp":"2026-03-10T09:35:01.893Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求诊断深渊代行者批注 API 的 502 错误。让我按照诊断步骤执行。\n\n502 错误通常意味着：\n1. 后端服务挂了\n2. Nginx 代理配置错误\n3. 端口冲突或未监听\n\n让我按步骤检查。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，诊断批注 API 502 错误。\n\n**步骤 1-2：检查服务状态和端口**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3711cfc6294c4245ab2aeb53","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"pm2 list && echo \"---\" && pm2 show abyss-annotation-api 2>&1 || echo \"服务不存在\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3a90d763701340258a036707","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ss -tlnp | grep 3002 || echo \"端口 3002 未监听\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":21318,"output":156,"cacheRead":7424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28898,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773135286404}}
